FAQs.markdown:
Check if your slideshow [`isPlaying`](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w.Slideshow.html#isPlaying). If it's playing, [`pause()`](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w.Slideshow.html#pause) the slideshow. If it's not playing, [`play()`](https://www.wix.com/velo/reference/$w.Slideshow.html#play) the slideshow.

```javascript

if($w("#myElement").isPlaying) {

  $w("#myElement").pause();

}

else {

  $w("#myElement").play();

}

```
